{
  "video_id": "eIdJ22AfsO8",
  "title": "What’s a smartphone made of? - Kim Preshoff",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6590.0,
      "end_time": 13501.0,
      "text": "As of 2018, there are around  2.5 billion smartphone users in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13502.0,
      "end_time": 15981.0,
      "text": "If we broke open all their newest phones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15981.0,
      "end_time": 19190.0,
      "text": "which are just a fraction  of the total that’ve been built,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19190.0,
      "end_time": 21110.0,
      "text": "and split them into their component parts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21110.0,
      "end_time": 24819.0,
      "text": "that would produce  around 85,000 kilograms of gold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24819.0,
      "end_time": 27150.0,
      "text": "875,000 of silver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27150.0,
      "end_time": 30285.0,
      "text": "and 40 million kilograms of copper."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30286.0,
      "end_time": 33410.0,
      "text": "How did this precious cache  get into our phones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33410.0,
      "end_time": 35300.0,
      "text": "and can we reclaim it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35300.0,
      "end_time": 38191.0,
      "text": "Gold, silver, and copper  are actually just a few"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38191.0,
      "end_time": 42509.0,
      "text": "of the 70 or so chemical elements  that make up the average smartphone."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42509.0,
      "end_time": 44562.0,
      "text": "These can be divided  into different groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44562.0,
      "end_time": 47590.0,
      "text": "two of the most critical  being rare earth elements"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47591.0,
      "end_time": 49311.0,
      "text": "and precious metals."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49311.0,
      "end_time": 54530.0,
      "text": "Rare earths are a selection of 17 elements that are actually common in Earth’s crust"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54530.0,
      "end_time": 58407.0,
      "text": "and are found in many areas across  the world in low concentrations."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58407.0,
      "end_time": 61248.0,
      "text": "These elements have a huge range of magnetic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61249.0,
      "end_time": 62201.0,
      "text": "phosphorescent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62201.0,
      "end_time": 63855.0,
      "text": "and conductive properties"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63855.0,
      "end_time": 66596.0,
      "text": "that make them crucial  to modern technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66596.0,
      "end_time": 69908.0,
      "text": "In fact, of the 17 types  of rare earth metals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69908.0,
      "end_time": 73757.0,
      "text": "phones and other electronics  may contain up to 16."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73757.0,
      "end_time": 77465.0,
      "text": "In smartphones, these create the screen  and color display,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77465.0,
      "end_time": 78915.0,
      "text": "aid conductivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78915.0,
      "end_time": 81393.0,
      "text": "and produce the signature vibrations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81393.0,
      "end_time": 82929.0,
      "text": "amongst other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82929.0,
      "end_time": 84872.0,
      "text": "And yet, crucial as they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84872.0,
      "end_time": 86815.0,
      "text": "extracting these elements from the earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86815.0,
      "end_time": 90660.0,
      "text": "is linked to some disturbing  environmental impacts."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90660.0,
      "end_time": 93124.0,
      "text": "Rare earth elements can often be found,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93124.0,
      "end_time": 94461.0,
      "text": "but in many areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94461.0,
      "end_time": 99429.0,
      "text": "it’s not economically feasible  to extract them due to low concentrations."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99430.0,
      "end_time": 100505.0,
      "text": "Much of the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100505.0,
      "end_time": 103949.0,
      "text": "extracting them requires  a method called open pit mining"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103950.0,
      "end_time": 106473.0,
      "text": "that exposes vast areas of land."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106473.0,
      "end_time": 110877.0,
      "text": "This form of mining destroys  huge swaths of natural habitats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110877.0,
      "end_time": 113800.0,
      "text": "and causes air and water pollution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 116226.0,
      "text": "threatening the health  of nearby communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 116227.0,
      "end_time": 118685.0,
      "text": "Another group of ingredients  in smartphones"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118685.0,
      "end_time": 121291.0,
      "text": "comes with similar environmental risks:"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121291.0,
      "end_time": 123285.0,
      "text": "these are metals such as copper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 123285.0,
      "end_time": 124256.0,
      "text": "silver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124256.0,
      "end_time": 125283.0,
      "text": "palladium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125283.0,
      "end_time": 126189.0,
      "text": "aluminum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 126189.0,
      "end_time": 127590.0,
      "text": "platinum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127600.0,
      "end_time": 127971.0,
      "text": "tungsten,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127971.0,
      "end_time": 128759.0,
      "text": "tin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 128758.00000000001,
      "end_time": 129495.00000000001,
      "text": "lead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 129496.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130478.00000000001,
      "text": "and gold."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130478.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131931.0,
      "text": "We also mine magnesium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 131931.0,
      "end_time": 132743.0,
      "text": "lithium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 132743.0,
      "end_time": 133646.0,
      "text": "silica,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 133646.0,
      "end_time": 135391.0,
      "text": "and potassium to make phones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 135391.0,
      "end_time": 139257.0,
      "text": "and all of it is associated  with vast habitat destruction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 139257.0,
      "end_time": 141603.0,
      "text": "as well as air and water pollution."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 141603.0,
      "end_time": 144764.0,
      "text": "Mining comes with  worrying social problems, too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 144764.0,
      "end_time": 148254.0,
      "text": "like large-scale human  and animal displacement"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 148254.0,
      "end_time": 150704.0,
      "text": "to make way for industrial operations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 150705.0,
      "end_time": 154438.0,
      "text": "and frequently,  poor working conditions for laborers."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 154438.0,
      "end_time": 158988.0,
      "text": "Lastly, phone production  also requires petroleum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 158989.0,
      "end_time": 161513.0,
      "text": "one of the main drivers of climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 161513.0,
      "end_time": 167223.0,
      "text": "That entwines our smartphones inextricably with this growing planetary conundrum."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 167223.0,
      "end_time": 168494.0,
      "text": "And, what’s more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168494.0,
      "end_time": 172142.0,
      "text": "the ingredients we mine  to make our phones aren’t infinite."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 172142.0,
      "end_time": 174367.0,
      "text": "One day, they’ll simply run out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 174367.0,
      "end_time": 178335.0,
      "text": "and we haven’t yet discovered effective  replacements for some."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 178336.0,
      "end_time": 179432.0,
      "text": "Despite this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 179432.0,
      "end_time": 182262.0,
      "text": "the number of smartphones  is on a steady increase;"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 182262.0,
      "end_time": 187779.0,
      "text": "by 2019 it’s predicted that  there’ll be close to 3 billion in use."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 187779.0,
      "end_time": 190936.0,
      "text": "This means that reclaiming the bounty  within our phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 190937.0,
      "end_time": 193507.0,
      "text": "is swiftly becoming a necessity."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 193507.0,
      "end_time": 195356.0,
      "text": "So, if you have an old phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 195356.0,
      "end_time": 198765.0,
      "text": "you might want to consider your options  before throwing it away."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 198765.0,
      "end_time": 202332.0,
      "text": "To minimize waste, you could donate it  to a charity for reuse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 202332.0,
      "end_time": 205750.0,
      "text": "take it to an e-waste recycling facility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 205750.0,
      "end_time": 208447.0,
      "text": "or look for a company  that refurbishes old models."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 208448.0,
      "end_time": 212171.0,
      "text": "However, even recycling companies  need our scrutiny."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 212171.0,
      "end_time": 214221.0,
      "text": "Just as the production of smartphones"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 214221.0,
      "end_time": 216816.0,
      "text": "comes with social  and environmental problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 216816.0,
      "end_time": 219850.0,
      "text": "dismantling them does too."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 219850.0,
      "end_time": 222554.0,
      "text": "E-waste is sometimes intentionally  exported to countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 222554.0,
      "end_time": 225980.0,
      "text": "where labor is cheap  but working conditions are poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 225980.0,
      "end_time": 229447.0,
      "text": "Vast workforces,  often made up of women and children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 229448.0,
      "end_time": 230809.0,
      "text": "may be underpaid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 230809.0,
      "end_time": 233528.0,
      "text": "lack the training  to safely disassemble phones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 233528.0,
      "end_time": 236555.0,
      "text": "and be exposed to elements  like lead and mercury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 236556.0,
      "end_time": 239692.0,
      "text": "which can permanently damage  their nervous systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 239692.0,
      "end_time": 242373.0,
      "text": "Phone waste can also end up  in huge dump sites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 242373.0,
      "end_time": 245561.0,
      "text": "leaching toxic chemicals  into the soil and water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 245562.0,
      "end_time": 249632.0,
      "text": "mirroring the problems of the mines  where the elements originated."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 249632.0,
      "end_time": 253568.0,
      "text": "A phone is much more than it appears  to be on the surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 253568.0,
      "end_time": 257320.0,
      "text": "It’s an assemblage of elements from multiple countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 257310.0,
      "end_time": 261840.0,
      "text": "linked to impacts  that are unfolding on a global scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 261839.99999999997,
      "end_time": 265390.0,
      "text": "So, until someone invents  a completely sustainable smartphone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 265400.0,
      "end_time": 266528.0,
      "text": "we’ll need to come to terms"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 266528.0,
      "end_time": 270543.0,
      "text": "with how this technology affects widespread places and people."
    }
  ]
}